snippet.title: Super Mario Bros. 35 - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
A competitive clash comes to the Mushroom Kingdom! Super Mario Bros. 35 is a competitive 35-player online battle where the last Mario standing wins! Beat courses while sending each other enemies you defeat! Coming 10/1 until 3/31 exclusively to Nintendo Switch Online.

https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/super-mario-bros-35-switch/
